data.description: Beautiful home ready to move. Home on Cul-De-Sac, Totally remodeled. Huge family room area. Enjoy the backyard with water view and privacy. Neighbors quite far away on both sides.  Located minutes away from Medical offices, restaurants, shopping centers, parks. No HOA  Please submit serious offers with buyer's proof of funds or approval letter to the listing agent. This property is not in foreclosure nor  is it up for auction.   The owner is willing to see reasonable offers.  On AS-iS FAR/BAR Contract. All room sizes and MLS information to be confirmed by buyer and buyers agent during inspection period.    **DON'T COORDINATE AN APPOINTMENT IF YOU DON'T SENT THE APPROVAL LETTER OR PROOF OF FUNDS IN THE BANK**
